Thought: Priya's email address is already found in the document, and a short summary is needed. The document already contains a summary of the evaluation, so I can use that as the short summary.
Action: send_email
Action Input: {"to": "priya@company.com", "body": "The procurement working group leans toward Vendor B (Acme Object Cloud) for the cloud storage evaluation. The ~33% price premium over Vendor A is justified by the wider EU region coverage and the inclusion of 24/7 support without an add-on."}
